title: Cam Newton leaves preseason game with foot injury (Football 8/23)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by the Pick Six SuperFriends to finish Fantasy Week. The guys recap Thursday night's Week 3 preseason games including an injury to Cam Newton and what it means for Carolina and fantasy owners, the performances of rookie QBs Dwayne Haskins and Daniel Jones and a totally weird game between the Packers and Raiders. Next, reports that the Cowboys have offered Ezekiel Elliott a contract that would make him the 2nd-highest paid RB in NFL, plus a look ahead at the rest of the preseason games slated for this weekend.
